<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>svasti</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> samastaprasvastisahitaṁbuna śrī
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ma<unclear>nmahā</unclear>maṁḍalēsvara kulōttuṁggarājē
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁdracōḍarājula rājyamuttarōttarā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>bhivriddhi<unclear>ṁ</unclear>gā sakavaruṣaṁbulu 1087
<lb n="5"/>nēṁṭi yuttarāyanasaṁkrā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>ttinimi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tyamunaṁ go<unclear>ṟi</unclear>paṟti sūrapanāyaku
<lb n="7"/>koḍuku kētināyakuṁḍu krōvi śrī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>bhīmēśvaramahādēvaraku nakhaṁḍa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>dīpamunaku niccina goṟiyalu 55 vīniṁ jē
<lb n="10" break="no"/>koni nanni<unclear>ya</unclear>bōyini koḍku bolle nitya māneṁḍu
<lb n="11"/>neyi vōsi tana putrānupavutrula
<lb n="12"/>vaṁśānukramaṁbuna nādityacaṁdrula kala
<lb n="13" break="no"/>yaṁtagālamu naḍapaṁgalavāru dīni nevvarēni vighnamu
<lb n="14"/>sēsinavāru gaṁggaka<unclear>ṛta</unclear> vēyu gavilala vadhiyiṁccinavāṁḍu
<lb n="15"/>vāranāsi vraccinavāṁḍu peddakodku kapālamunaṁ guḍicinavā
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ṁḍu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svadattaṁ paradattaṁ <unclear>vā yō</unclear> harēta vasuṁdhara <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> ṣaṣṭirvvaruṣasa
<lb n="17" break="no"/>hasrāṇi viṣṭāyāṁ jāyate krimi<unclear>ḥ</unclear> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśrīśrī [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>] 
</p>

